# Jobber API to Looker Studio Integration

## Overview
This project integrates **Jobber API** with **Looker Studio** to enable **automated data visualization**. It fetches data via API, processes it in Google Sheets, and connects it to Looker Studio.

## Features
‚úÖ OAuth 2.0 authentication  
‚úÖ Automated token refresh  
‚úÖ Google Apps Script for API calls  
‚úÖ Google Sheets as a data store  
‚úÖ Looker Studio dashboard integration  

